<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Saint Joseph Jaipur School</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Poppins,sans-serif}

body{
color:#0b3d2e;
background:linear-gradient(270deg,#e8f5e9,#c8e6c9,#a5d6a7,#e8f5e9);
background-size:800% 800%;
animation:gradientMove 18s ease infinite;
scroll-behavior:smooth;
}

@keyframes gradientMove{
0%{background-position:0% 50%}
50%{background-position:100% 50%}
100%{background-position:0% 50%}
}

.menu-btn{
position:fixed;
top:20px;
left:20px;
background:#064e3b;
color:white;
border:none;
padding:10px 16px;
font-size:18px;
cursor:pointer;
border-radius:6px;
z-index:1200;
}

.sidebar{
position:fixed;
left:0;
top:0;
height:100%;
width:260px;
background:#064e3b;
padding-top:20px;
transform:translateX(-260px);
transition:0.4s;
z-index:1000;
}

.sidebar.active{transform:translateX(0)}

.logo-space{
height:120px;
margin:10px;
border:2px dashed #ffffff88;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
color:white;
font-size:14px;
text-align:center;
}

.sidebar a{
display:block;
color:white;
padding:14px 25px;
text-decoration:none;
transition:0.3s;
}

.sidebar a:hover{background:#0f766e}

section{
min-height:100vh;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
padding:60px 10%;
}

.content{width:100%}

h1,h2{color:#064e3b;margin-bottom:20px;text-align:center}

.card{
background:white;
padding:35px;
border-radius:14px;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
max-width:1000px;
margin:auto;
line-height:1.7;
transition:0.3s;
}

.card:hover{transform:translateY(-6px)}

.grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:20px;
}

.gallery img{
width:100%;
border-radius:10px;
transition:0.4s;
}

.gallery img:hover{transform:scale(1.08)}

/* IMAGE SLIDER */
.slider{
position:relative;
max-width:1000px;
margin:auto;
overflow:hidden;
border-radius:14px;
}

.slides{
display:flex;
transition:0.6s;
}

.slides img{
width:100%;
flex-shrink:0;
}

/* NOTICE BOARD */
.notice-board{
background:#f1f8f4;
border-left:6px solid #064e3b;
padding:20px;
margin-top:20px;
border-radius:10px;
}

.notice-board ul{
padding-left:20px;
}

.notice-board li{margin:8px 0}

/* EVENT CALENDAR */
.calendar{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
gap:15px;
margin-top:20px;
}

.calendar div{
background:#e8f5e9;
padding:15px;
border-radius:10px;
text-align:center;
font-weight:500;
}

form input,form textarea,form select{
width:100%;
padding:12px;
margin-top:10px;
border:1px solid #ccc;
border-radius:8px;
}

form button{
margin-top:15px;
padding:12px;
border:none;
background:#064e3b;
color:white;
border-radius:8px;
cursor:pointer;
transition:0.3s;
}

form button:hover{background:#0f766e}

footer{
text-align:center;
padding:30px;
background:#064e3b;
color:white;
}

/* WHATSAPP BUTTON */
.whatsapp{
position:fixed;
bottom:25px;
right:25px;
background:#25D366;
color:white;
padding:14px 18px;
border-radius:50px;
font-size:18px;
text-decoration:none;
box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}

@media(max-width:768px){
section{padding:80px 6%}
.calendar{grid-template-columns:1fr}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<button class="menu-btn" onclick="toggleMenu()">☰ Menu</button>

<div class="sidebar" id="sidebar">

<div class="logo-space">
<img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAA..." style="max-width:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:contain;border-radius:6px;">
</div>

<a href="#home">Home</a>
<a href="#about">About</a>
<a href="#principal">Principal</a>
<a href="#director">Director</a>
<a href="#sports">Sports</a>
<a href="#admission">Admissions</a>
<a href="#gallery">Gallery</a>
<a href="#events">Events</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>

</div>

<div class="content">

<section id="home">
<div class="card">
<h1>Welcome to Saint Joseph Jaipur School</h1>

<div class="slider">
<div class="slides" id="slides">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1588072432836-e10032774350">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503676260728-1c00da094a0b">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523240795612-9a054b0db644">
</div>
</div>

<p style="margin-top:20px">A place where young minds grow, dreams begin, and futures are shaped. Our school provides quality education for students from Nursery to Class IX.</p>

<div class="notice-board">
<h3>School Notice Board</h3>
<ul>
<li>Admissions open for 2026 session</li>
<li>New session coming soon</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
</section>

<section id="about">
<div class="card">
<h2>About Us</h2>
<p>Saint Joseph Jaipur School is committed to quality education and holistic development for students from Nursery to Class IX. Our goal is to nurture discipline, creativity, and strong moral values.</p>
</div>
</section>

<section id="principal">
<div class="card">
<h2>Principal's Message</h2>
<p>Our institution is committed to providing quality education that nurtures academic excellence and moral values while building confidence and leadership in every student.</p>
</div>
</section>

<section id="director">
<div class="card">
<h2>Director's Message</h2>
<p>Education shapes the future of individuals and society. Our vision is to create a learning environment where students grow intellectually and socially.</p>
</div>
</section>

<section id="sports">
<div class="card">
<h2>Sports</h2>
<p>Sports activities help students develop teamwork, discipline, and leadership. Our school encourages active participation in physical activities.</p>
</div>
</section>

<section id="admission">
<div class="card">
<h2>Admission Form</h2>
<form>
<h3>Student Details</h3>
<input placeholder="Student Name">
<input type="date">
<select>
<option>Select Class</option>
<option>Nursery</option>
<option>KG</option>
<option>Class 1</option>
<option>Class 2</option>
<option>Class 3</option>
<option>Class 4</option>
<option>Class 5</option>
<option>Class 6</option>
<option>Class 7</option>
<option>Class 8</option>
<option>Class 9</option>
</select>

<h3>Aadhar Details</h3>
<input placeholder="Aadhar Card Number">
<label>Upload Aadhar Card Photocopy</label>
<input type="file">

<h3>Certificates</h3>
<label>Birth Certificate</label>
<input type="file">
<label>Caste Certificate</label>
<input type="file">

<h3>Parent Details</h3>
<input placeholder="Father Name">
<input placeholder="Father Phone Number">
<input placeholder="Father Occupation">
<input placeholder="Mother Name">
<input placeholder="Mother Phone Number">
<input placeholder="Mother Occupation">
<textarea placeholder="Parent Address"></textarea>
<button>Submit Application</button>
</form>
</div>
</section>

<section id="gallery">
<div class="card">
<h2>Gallery</h2>
<div class="grid gallery">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1588072432836-e10032774350">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503676260728-1c00da094a0b">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523240795612-9a054b0db644">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580582932707-520aed937b7b">
</div>
</div>
</section>

<section id="events">
<div class="card">
<h2>Events Calendar</h2>
<div class="calendar">
<div>Jan 26<br>Republic Day</div>
<div>Feb 15<br>Science Exhibition</div>
<div>Mar 10<br>Sports Day</div>
<div>Aug 15<br>Independence Day</div>
<div>Sep 05<br>Teachers Day</div>
<div>Dec 20<br>Annual Day</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<section id="contact">
<div class="card">
<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>Phone: 9602118565</p>
<p>Address: 21 Dev Vihar Colony, Near Dhani Kumawatan, Muhana Mod, Sanganer, Jaipur (Rajasthan)</p>
</div>
</section>

</div>

<footer>
© 2026 Saint Joseph Jaipur School
</footer>

<a class="whatsapp" href="https://wa.me/919602118565" target="_blank">WhatsApp</a>

<script>
function toggleMenu(){
 document.getElementById('sidebar').classList.toggle('active');
}

let index=0;
const slides=document.getElementById("slides");
setInterval(()=>{
 index=(index+1)%3;
 slides.style.transform=`translateX(-${index*100}%)`;
},3000);
</script>

</body>
</html>
